<div class="language-yaml codeBlockContainer_A7XW theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_ACY8"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yaml codeBlock_EBFy thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_AOuX"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">steps</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> Generate summary</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">run</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">|</span><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#e3116c"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#e3116c">      echo &quot;## Build Summary&quot; &gt;&gt; &quot;$ATOMGIT_STEP_SUMMARY&quot;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#e3116c">      echo &quot;Build is running...&quot; &gt;&gt; &quot;$ATOMGIT_STEP_SUMMARY&quot;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      echo &quot;</span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">## Build Summary&quot; &gt; &quot;$ATOMGIT_STEP_SUMMARY&quot;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      echo &quot;Build failed. Please check logs.&quot; </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">&gt;</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">&gt;</span><span class="token plain"> &quot;$ATOMGIT_STEP_SUMMARY&quot;</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_uBn1"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_VsDu" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_AGYV"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_jkJu"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>For summary, <code>&gt;&gt;</code> means appending content, while <code>&gt;</code> means overwriting the content already written in the current step. If you want to completely delete the summary of the current step, you can delete the file pointed to by <code>ATOMGIT_STEP_SUMMARY</code>. After the step completes, the summary will be uploaded, and subsequent steps cannot modify the summary uploaded by previous steps.</p></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col col--12"></div></div></article><div class="row"><div class="col col--12"><nav class="pagination-nav docusaurus-mt-lg" aria-label="文件选项卡"><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--prev" href="/en/docs/help/home/org_project/pipeline/action-development/top-level-fields"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Previous Page</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Top-level Fields</div></a><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--next" href="/en/docs/help/home/org_project/pipeline/action-development/plugin-development-guide"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Next Page</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Plugin Development Guide</div></a></nav></div></div></div></div><div class="col col--3"><div class="tableOfContents_JiLI thin-scrollbar theme-doc-toc-desktop"><ul class="table-of-contents table-of-contents__left-border"><li><a href="#pipeline-system-variables" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Pipeline System Variables</a></li><li><a href="#contexts" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Contexts</a></li><li><a href="#runtime-process-file-instructions" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Runtime Process File Instructions</a></li><li><a href="#1-full-list-of-process-files" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">1. Full List of Process Files</a></li><li><a href="#2-atomgit_env-setting-environment-variables-for-subsequent-steps" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">2. <code>ATOMGIT_ENV</code>: Setting Environment Variables for Subse